      </ul>
      </p>
      <p class="my-4">
      In my <span class="font-bold">first week</span> at Tailwind Labs, I'll become more familiar with the community and understand the product areas. In my <span class="font-bold">first month</span>, I'll have fixed a bug or two and contribute to planning sessions. In my <span class="font-bold">first quarter</span> I'll have worked on a proposal for the broader adoption of Tailwind CSS' v4.x configuration improvements, and explore the implementation of a design token library for improved maintenance of <code>src/corePlugins.js</code>.   
